====Proper noun====
'''Jesus'''

# Jesus of [[Nazareth]], a [[Torah]]-observant [[Jewish]] man whom [[Christian]]s name [[Jesus Christ]] in belief that he is the [[Messiah]]. The actual English translation of the name is most likely [[Joshua]].

====Interjection====
# An expletive, whose use is considered [[blasphemous]] in some Christian [[sect]]s.

